data.text:
16 Episodes 2018 - 2018

Season 6 of this drama series opens with New Year's Eve on the horizon and Deacon (Charles Esten) feeling lonely. Juliette (Hayden Panettiere) has an onstage meltdown and finds help from a mysterious and unlikely source when Darius (Josh Stamberg) comes to her aid. Meanwhile, Gunnar (Sam Palladio) and Scarlett (Clare Bowen) are having a hard time working as solo artists. Plus, Maddie (Lennon Stella) meets Jonah Ford (Nick Luken), an up-and-coming young artist.
